name: 🥀 Tending The Garden
description:
"🥀 Tending The Garden" by Bryant W

Painted back around 2010 to express my life falling apart around me.

A depiction of my guts falling out every step of the way through life... leaving me having to pick them up just as quickly as they fell.

This is the physical painting (now NFT) expressing the need inside myself to find an ability to speak the truth and openly spill my guts and feelings out into the world.
